OL,3,CGrieving mum speaks out as the number
OL,4,Cof Ketamine deaths rises by 100k
OL,6,FA bereaved mother has vowed to "shout
OL,7,Ffrom the rooftops" about the dangers
OL,8,Fof ketamine use, after her daughter
OL,9,Fdied with significant internal damage
OL,10,Fcaused by the drug.
OL,12,FNatalie Ashton's 25-year-old daughter,
OL,13,FBeth, died in November 2024, having
OL,14,Fused the drug for six years following
OL,15,Fthe traumatic stillbirth of her baby
OL,16,Fboy in 2019.
OL,18,FWhile a post-mortem examination was
OL,19,Finconclusive on the immediate cause of
OL,20,Fdeath, it did confirm the devastating
OL,21,Flong-term impact of taking ketamine.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
