OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F399A1765719278
OL,3,CGrieving mum speaks out as the number
OL,4,Cof Ketamine deaths rises by 100k
OL,6,F"She started losing a dramatic amount
OL,7,Fof weight and I thought she had an
OL,8,Feating disorder. To me it was the only
OL,9,Flogical thing that I could think of to
OL,10,Fexplain the weight loss."
OL,12,FBeth had been referred for treatment
OL,13,Fand she "wanted the help, she wanted
OL,14,Fto get better... but the waiting times
OL,15,Fare so long" her heartbroken mum said.
OL,17,F"If she was in a different area, maybe
OL,18,Fshe would have got the treatment and
OL,19,Fmaybe they would have done scans, and,
OL,20,Fyou know, she could have still been
OL,21,Fhere."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
