OL,3,CGrieving mum speaks out as the number
OL,4,Cof Ketamine deaths rises by 100k
OL,6,FNatalie has created West Lancs
OL,7,FKetamine Awareness on Facebook which
OL,8,Faims to be a safe space for parents
OL,9,Fand families providing honest
OL,10,Finformation and support with the
OL,11,Fpromise of no stigma.
OL,13,F"Beth must have been so frightened,"
OL,14,FNatalie went on. "And that's what I
OL,15,Fthink about, how much pain she was in,
OL,16,Fnot just emotionally, but physically.
OL,18,F"And I didn't have any idea. I didn't
OL,19,Fgrasp that until after she was gone,
OL,20,Fand I was speaking to other people in
OL,21,Frecovery.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
