OL,3,CGrieving mum speaks out as the number
OL,4,Cof Ketamine deaths rises by 100k
OL,6,F"But that's what fuels me right now. I
OL,7,Fcan't let any other family go through
OL,8,Fthat."
OL,10,FFigures out today show that ketamine
OL,11,Fuse among 16-59 year-olds has remained
OL,12,Fbroadly similar to last year.
OL,14,FBut over the past decade, the number
OL,15,Fof people estimated to be using
OL,16,Fketamine has risen by over a hundred
OL,17,Fthousand.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
