OL,3,CGrieving mum speaks out as the number
OL,4,Cof Ketamine deaths rises by 100k
OL,6,FThe data is limited as it excludes
OL,7,Funder 16s at a time when ketamine use
OL,8,Famong younger people is of growing
OL,9,Fconcern.
OL,11,FWhile the amount of ketamine users has
OL,12,Fremained relatively unchanged in
OL,13,Frecent years, the numbers seeking
OL,14,Ftreatment has increased by 272% in the
OL,15,Fpast five years.
OL,17,FOver a ten-year period, the rise is
OL,18,Feven starker: treatment numbers have
OL,19,Fgrown twelve-fold, from 426 in 2014`15
OL,20,Fto 5,365 now.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
