OL,3,CGrieving mum speaks out as the number
OL,4,Cof Ketamine deaths rises by 100k
OL,6,FKetamine is considered a Class B drug
OL,7,Fbut the UK government is currently
OL,8,Fseeking advice from the Advisory
OL,9,FCouncil on the Misuse of Drugs (ACMD)
OL,10,Fon whether it should be reclassified
OL,11,Fto a Class A drug.
OL,13,FWith reports of some children as young
OL,14,Fas 10 getting their hands on it,
OL,15,FNatalie is in support of
OL,16,Freclassification.
OL,18,FShe said: "It's breaking that stigma
OL,19,Fand getting people talking.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
