OL,3,CGrieving mum speaks out as the number
OL,4,Cof Ketamine deaths rises by 100k
OL,6,F"And you know, we're parents. We need
OL,7,Fwe need this this information.
OL,9,F"We need to be armed with everything
OL,10,Fpossible to to protect our babies and
OL,11,Fkeep them safe."
OL,13,FEmma Foster is the service manager at
OL,14,FInspire in Lancashire, which supports
OL,15,Fpeople to take control of their
OL,16,Frelationship with drugs or alcohol.
OL,18,FShe urged people who think they need
OL,19,Fsupport to "reach out and get help".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
