OL,3,CGrieving mum speaks out as the number
OL,4,Cof Ketamine deaths rises by 100k
OL,6,FShe said: "The sooner that someone can
OL,7,Fdo that, the better.
OL,9,F"What we're seeing in services is
OL,10,Fpeople reaching out when they're
OL,11,Falready experiencing the physical
OL,12,Fhealth complications of using ketamine
OL,13,Ffor maybe a longer period of time.
OL,15,F"And that can be much more complex in
OL,16,Fterms of supporting somebody to manage
OL,17,Fthat, and it can often be a crisis
OL,18,Fintervention point.
OL,20,F"So my main message would just be to
OL,21,Freach out and ask for help earlier."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
